      <title>共和党议员敦促拜登停用竞选 TikTok 账户</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/republican-lawmakers-urge-biden-deactivate-campaign-tiktok-account-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由 18 名共和党议员组成的团体以国家安全为由，敦促总统乔·拜登停用其竞选团队的 TikTok 账户。]]></description>
