      <title>前线岛屿紧张局势升级，台湾驱逐中国海警船</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-china-coast-guard-triggers-panic-by-boarding-taiwan-tourist-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾周二驱逐了一艘进入其敏感前线岛屿附近海域的中国海警船，一天前，中国海警登上一艘台湾旅游船，台湾一位部长称这引发了“恐慌”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-minister-says-china-coast-guard-triggers-panic-by-boarding-taiwan-tourist-2024-02-20/</guid>
