      <title>关于Currys，英国连锁店中国京东和美国基金Elliott争夺</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/all-about-currys-uk-chain-chinas-jdcom-us-fund-elliott-vie-2024-02-19/</link>
